scenes.description: Mori Calliope walks through an underworld garden, discussing memories and avatar features.
Mori explores architecture and statues, speculating about the identity of a "Muse Calliope" statue.
Mori reaches an overlook showing a deserted city and points out the "Hell Temple."
Mori crosses a bridge while reminiscing about her past VR concerts and finds a camera interaction.
A sweeping camera view of the temple interior, which Mori recognizes from her "JIGOKU 6" performance.
Mori meets Jimodori, who is exhausted from climbing the stairs, and they have a humorous interaction.
